      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "内西皮导板",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "君臣们手挽手出了都城，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05024013_e00065",
      "play_id": "05024013",
      "scene_id": "05024013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "刘备、庞统、诸葛亮、关平同上。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05024013_e00066",
      "play_id": "05024013",
      "scene_id": "05024013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "尊一声刘主爷细听分明：汉高祖夺天下全凭韩信，有几个文武臣齐把功成。此一去阳平关山路险峻，切不可离却了刘封、关平。叫人来看过了御酒一樽，但愿得此一去马到功成。",
      "text_length": 78
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05024013_e00067",
      "play_id": "05024013",
      "scene_id": "05024013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "接过了军师爷御酒一樽，再将这荆州事托付先生。有东吴和北魏是孤旧恨，望先生你那里总要扫平。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05024013_e00068",
      "play_id": "05024013",
      "scene_id": "05024013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "蒙主公在长亭叮咛嘱咐，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05024013_e00069",
      "play_id": "05024013",
      "scene_id": "05024013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "酒来。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05024013_e00070",
      "play_id": "05024013",
      "scene_id": "05024013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "四下手"
      ],
      "text": "呵。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05024013_e00071",
      "play_id": "05024013",
      "scene_id": "05024013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 71,
